{
  "format": "paper",
  "version": 1,
  "savedAt": "2026-03-12T03:11:47.214Z",
  "document": {
    "titleHtml": "Welcome to Whitepaper (v0.1)",
    "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"page-assist\" data-page-assist=\"true\" data-page-kind=\"header\" data-page-index=\"1\" data-align=\"left\" data-placeholder=\"Header\" aria-label=\"Header for page 1\" style=\"text-align: left; position: absolute; top: -143px; left: -75px; right: -75px; width: auto; margin: 0px; z-index: 6;\" data-page-number-auto=\"true\" data-page-number-format=\"page\" data-page-assist-positioned=\"true\">Page 1</div><p></p><p></p><h2><span style=\"font-size: 20pt;\">What is Whitepaper?</span></h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Whitepaper is an <b>in progress</b>&nbsp;minimalist&nbsp;document editor that strips down writing&nbsp;for you and aims to keep most of the navigation in the keyboard. One unique part&nbsp;about Whitepaper is that there&nbsp;is no visible UI, instead it uses a myriad of keyboard shortcuts and inline text. This document will help outline all the features of the software.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><h2>Basic Controls</h2><p></p><h3>Interaction Menu</h3><p></p><p>Instead of a bar at the top like word has, Whitepaper has an <b>interaction menu </b>toggled by <b>double tapping shift</b>. You can navigate this menu by <b>tapping tab</b> to go forward or the <b>left and right arrow keys</b>. The interaction menu can be deactivated using the escape key or double tapping shift again. The interaction menu contains most text related actions you will need including <b>bold, </b><u>underline,</u>&nbsp;<i>italics, </i><strike>strikethrough, </strike><sup>superscript</sup><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;,&nbsp;<sub>subscript&nbsp; ,</sub></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">bullets and more!</span></p><p></p><h3>Page Formatting</h3><p>Similar to LaTeX, whitepaper uses the commands \\ subtitle, \\ section, \\ subsection and&nbsp;\\ subsubsection in order to create different headings. You can see the various sections in your document by holding <b>Tab </b>and using the <b>arrow keys</b>&nbsp;to navigate between sections. <b>Control + M </b>opens the <b>Metadata Menu</b>&nbsp;where you can choose various page related settings including the citation format, page size, orientation and margin size. You can also add inline latex with the dollar sign like this&nbsp;<span class=\"latex-token\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-latex=\"\\alpha + \\beta = \\gamma\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>α</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>β</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>γ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\alpha + \\beta = \\gamma</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6667em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0037em;\">α</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.8889em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0528em;\">β</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.625em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0556em;\">γ</span></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>To access <b>page numbers</b>, <b>headers</b> and <b>footers </b>hover your mouse over the top corner of any page to edit its specific header or footer. The header and footers stay consistent from page to page (except the first)&nbsp;unless manually edited</p><h3 style=\"\">Inlines</h3><p style=\"\">\\ cite opens up your bibliography where you can add citations which appear on the last page of the document<span class=\"citation-marker\" data-cite-id=\"cite-mlrfq586-om6ey\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-cite-order=\"1\">1</span> </p><div class=\"page-assist\" data-page-assist=\"true\" data-page-kind=\"header\" data-page-index=\"2\" data-align=\"left\" data-placeholder=\"Header\" data-page-repeat-auto=\"true\" aria-label=\"Header for page 2\" data-page-number-auto=\"true\" style=\"text-align: left; position: absolute; top: 979px; left: -75px; right: -75px; width: auto; margin: 0px; z-index: 6;\" data-page-number-format=\"page\" data-page-assist-positioned=\"true\">Page 2</div><p style=\"\">\\ graph allows you to insert a basic plot and you can paste CSV or cell rows and columns for ease of insertion, click out in order to exit menu </p><p></p><figure class=\"graph-block\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\" data-graph-state=\"{&quot;chartTitle&quot;:&quot;Sample Graph&quot;,&quot;xTitle&quot;:&quot;X Axis&quot;,&quot;yTitle&quot;:&quot;Y Axis&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Graph caption&quot;,&quot;grid&quot;:true,&quot;x&quot;:[&quot;1&quot;,&quot;2&quot;,&quot;3&quot;,&quot;4&quot;],&quot;series&quot;:[{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Series 1&quot;,&quot;values&quot;:[2,4,3,6]}]}\" draggable=\"true\" data-graph-bound=\"true\" style=\"\"><div class=\"graph-chart-wrap\"><svg class=\"graph-svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 620 320\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" aria-label=\"Graph\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 620 / 320; min-height: 220px;\"><g stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"0.8\" opacity=\"0.34\"><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"264\" x2=\"478\" y2=\"264\"></line><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"207.5\" x2=\"478\" y2=\"207.5\"></line><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"151\" x2=\"478\" y2=\"151\"></line><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"94.5\" x2=\"478\" y2=\"94.5\"></line><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"478\" y2=\"38\"></line><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"68\" y2=\"264\"></line><line x1=\"204.66666666666666\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"204.66666666666666\" y2=\"264\"></line><line x1=\"341.3333333333333\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"341.3333333333333\" y2=\"264\"></line><line x1=\"478\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"478\" y2=\"264\"></line></g><g stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" fill=\"none\"><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"264\" x2=\"478\" y2=\"264\"></line><line x1=\"68\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"68\" y2=\"264\"></line></g><g fill=\"#000000\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Times New Roman\"><text x=\"60\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"end\">2</text><text x=\"60\" y=\"211.5\" text-anchor=\"end\">3</text><text x=\"60\" y=\"155\" text-anchor=\"end\">4</text><text x=\"60\" y=\"98.5\" text-anchor=\"end\">5</text><text x=\"60\" y=\"42\" text-anchor=\"end\">6</text></g><g fill=\"#000000\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Times New Roman\"><text x=\"68\" y=\"280\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"204.66666666666666\" y=\"280\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"341.3333333333333\" y=\"280\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"478\" y=\"280\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text></g><path d=\"M 68 264 L 204.66666666666666 151 L 341.3333333333333 207.5 L 478 38\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-dasharray=\"\"></path><circle cx=\"68\" cy=\"264\" r=\"3.2\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"1.1\" class=\"graph-hover-point\" data-series=\"Series 1\" data-label=\"1\" data-value=\"2\"></circle><circle cx=\"204.66666666666666\" cy=\"151\" r=\"3.2\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"1.1\" class=\"graph-hover-point\" data-series=\"Series 1\" data-label=\"2\" data-value=\"4\"></circle><circle cx=\"341.3333333333333\" cy=\"207.5\" r=\"3.2\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"1.1\" class=\"graph-hover-point\" data-series=\"Series 1\" data-label=\"3\" data-value=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"478\" cy=\"38\" r=\"3.2\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"1.1\" class=\"graph-hover-point\" data-series=\"Series 1\" data-label=\"4\" data-value=\"6\"></circle><rect x=\"488\" y=\"44\" width=\"110\" height=\"34\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"1\"></rect><g fill=\"#000000\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Times New Roman\"><line x1=\"498\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"524\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"#000000\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-dasharray=\"\"></line><text x=\"532\" y=\"64\">Series 1</text></g><text x=\"310\" y=\"20\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#000000\" font-size=\"16\" font-family=\"Times New Roman\" font-weight=\"700\">Sample Graph</text><text x=\"310\" y=\"308\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#000000\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Times New Roman\">X Axis</text><text x=\"16\" y=\"160\" transform=\"rotate(-90 16 160)\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#000000\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Times New Roman\">Y Axis</text></svg><div class=\"graph-tooltip\"></div></div><figcaption class=\"graph-caption-line\"><span class=\"graph-figure-number\">Figure 1.</span><span class=\"graph-caption-text\">Graph caption</span></figcaption><div class=\"graph-settings\">\n    <div class=\"graph-settings-row\">\n      <label class=\"graph-setting\">\n        <span>Chart title</span>\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-input graph-input-chart-title\" placeholder=\"Enter chart title\">\n      </label>\n      <label class=\"graph-setting\">\n        <span>Caption</span>\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-input graph-input-caption\" placeholder=\"Enter figure caption\">\n      </label>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"graph-settings-row\">\n      <label class=\"graph-setting\">\n        <span>X axis title</span>\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-input graph-input-x-title\" placeholder=\"X axis label\">\n      </label>\n      <label class=\"graph-setting\">\n        <span>Y axis title</span>\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-input graph-input-y-title\" placeholder=\"Y axis label\">\n      </label>\n      <label class=\"graph-setting\"><span>Chart type</span><select class=\"graph-input graph-input-chart-type\"><option value=\"line\">Line</option><option value=\"bar\">Bar</option><option value=\"scatter\">Scatter</option></select></label><label class=\"graph-toggle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"graph-input-grid\">\n        <span>Grid</span>\n      </label>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet\" data-axis=\"x\">\n      <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-header\">\n        <span class=\"graph-spreadsheet-title\">X Axis Values</span>\n        <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-actions\">\n          <button type=\"button\" data-spreadsheet-action=\"add-point\">+ Point</button>\n          <button type=\"button\" data-spreadsheet-action=\"remove-point\">− Point</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-grid\"><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\"><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"1\" data-row=\"0\" data-col=\"0\"></div><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\"><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"2\" data-row=\"1\" data-col=\"1\"></div><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\"><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"3\" data-row=\"2\" data-col=\"2\"></div><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\"><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"4\" data-row=\"3\" data-col=\"3\"></div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet\" data-axis=\"y\">\n      <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-header\">\n        <span class=\"graph-spreadsheet-title\">Series Data</span>\n        <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-actions\">\n          <button type=\"button\" data-spreadsheet-action=\"add-series\">+ Series</button>\n          <button type=\"button\" data-spreadsheet-action=\"remove-series\">− Series</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-grid\"><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row graph-spreadsheet-row-header\"><span class=\"graph-cell-header graph-cell-corner\">X</span><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell graph-cell-series-name\" placeholder=\"Series 1\" data-series-index=\"0\" data-row=\"-1\" data-col=\"0\"></div><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\" data-x-index=\"0\"><span class=\"graph-cell-header graph-cell-corner graph-cell-x-label\">1</span><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"0\" data-row=\"0\" data-col=\"0\" data-series-index=\"0\" inputmode=\"decimal\"></div><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\" data-x-index=\"1\"><span class=\"graph-cell-header graph-cell-corner graph-cell-x-label\">2</span><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"0\" data-row=\"1\" data-col=\"0\" data-series-index=\"0\" inputmode=\"decimal\"></div><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\" data-x-index=\"2\"><span class=\"graph-cell-header graph-cell-corner graph-cell-x-label\">3</span><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"0\" data-row=\"2\" data-col=\"0\" data-series-index=\"0\" inputmode=\"decimal\"></div><div class=\"graph-spreadsheet-row\" data-x-index=\"3\"><span class=\"graph-cell-header graph-cell-corner graph-cell-x-label\">4</span><input type=\"text\" class=\"graph-cell\" placeholder=\"0\" data-row=\"3\" data-col=\"0\" data-series-index=\"0\" inputmode=\"decimal\"></div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"graph-paste-area\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"graph-paste-toggle\" data-graph-paste=\"toggle\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Paste table data</button>\n      <div class=\"graph-paste-panel\">\n        <textarea class=\"graph-table-textarea\" spellcheck=\"false\" placeholder=\"Paste CSV data here\"></textarea>\n        <div class=\"graph-table-actions\">\n          <button type=\"button\" data-graph-table=\"apply-x\">Apply as X</button>\n          <button type=\"button\" data-graph-table=\"apply-y\">Apply as Series</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div></figure><p>\\ image allows you to add an Image from your computer, dragging and dropping should also work here.</p><p></p><figure class=\"image-block\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\" data-image-align=\"center\" data-image-wrap=\"break\" data-image-width=\"42\" style=\"--image-width: 42%;\" draggable=\"true\" data-image-bound=\"true\"><div class=\"image-media-wrap\"><img class=\"image-element\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-18 at 12.35.55 AM.png\"></div><figcaption class=\"image-caption-line\"><span class=\"image-figure-number\">Figure 2.</span><span class=\"image-caption-text\">Image caption</span></figcaption><div class=\"image-settings\">\n    <div class=\"image-settings-row\">\n      <label class=\"image-setting image-setting-wide\">\n        <span>Caption</span>\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"image-input image-input-caption\" placeholder=\"Enter figure caption\">\n      </label>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"image-settings-row\">\n      <div class=\"image-button-group\">\n        <span>Align</span>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-choice\" data-image-align=\"left\">Left</button>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-choice is-selected\" data-image-align=\"center\">Center</button>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-choice\" data-image-align=\"right\">Right</button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"image-button-group\">\n        <span>Wrap</span>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-choice is-selected\" data-image-wrap=\"break\">Block</button>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-choice\" data-image-wrap=\"left\">Left</button>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-choice\" data-image-wrap=\"right\">Right</button>\n      </div>\n      <label class=\"image-setting image-setting-width\">\n        <span class=\"image-width-label\">Width</span>\n        <input type=\"range\" class=\"image-input-width\" min=\"20\" max=\"100\" step=\"0.5\">\n        <span class=\"image-width-value\">42%</span>\n      </label>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"image-settings-row image-settings-actions\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-action-btn\" data-image-action=\"replace\">Replace</button>\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"image-action-btn\" data-image-action=\"remove\">Remove</button>\n    </div>\n  </div></figure><table class=\"editor-table\" data-paper-table=\"true\" draggable=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><caption class=\"editor-table-caption\">Table 1. Fun Tables</caption><tbody><tr><th>Header 1</th><th>Header 2</th><th>Header 3</th><th data-table-stat-col=\"row-mean\">Mean</th></tr><tr><td data-table-uncertainty=\"true\">1 +/- 1</td><td data-table-uncertainty=\"true\">2 +/- 1</td><td data-table-uncertainty=\"true\">3 +/- 1</td><td data-table-stat-col=\"row-mean\">2</td></tr><tr><td data-table-uncertainty=\"true\">2 +/- 2</td><td data-table-uncertainty=\"true\">4 +/- 2</td><td data-table-uncertainty=\"true\">6 +/- 2</td><td data-table-stat-col=\"row-mean\">4</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"media-clear-paragraph\" style=\"\"><br></p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"\"></p><h2 style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 26.6667px;\">File and Media Management&nbsp;</span></h2><p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Command + S allows you to save in either the .paper, .docx or .pdf formats. </span><b style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">You will need to save in .paper in order to continue editing your whitepaper.</b></p><p></p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Command + O allows you to open a .paper file of your choosing from your file manager</span></p><div class=\"page-assist\" data-page-assist=\"true\" data-page-kind=\"header\" data-page-index=\"3\" data-align=\"left\" data-placeholder=\"Header\" data-page-repeat-auto=\"true\" aria-label=\"Header for page 3\" data-page-number-auto=\"true\" style=\"text-align: left; position: absolute; top: 2101px; left: -75px; right: -75px; width: auto; margin: 0px; z-index: 6;\" data-page-number-format=\"page\" data-page-assist-positioned=\"true\">Page 3</div><p style=\"\">Control + \\ opens the media management menu which allows you drag and drop tables, graphs and images so that you can insert them somewhere else, give it a try!</p><p style=\"\"><br></p><p style=\"\"><br></p><p></p><p></p><div class=\"page-assist\" data-page-assist=\"true\" data-page-kind=\"note\" data-page-index=\"1\" data-align=\"right\" data-placeholder=\"Page note\" aria-label=\"Page note for page 1\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><br></div><div class=\"page-assist\" data-page-assist=\"true\" data-page-kind=\"note\" data-page-index=\"1\" data-align=\"right\" data-placeholder=\"Page note\" aria-label=\"Page note for page 1\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><br></div><div class=\"page-assist\" data-page-assist=\"true\" data-page-kind=\"header\" data-page-index=\"4\" data-align=\"left\" data-placeholder=\"Header\" data-page-repeat-auto=\"true\" aria-label=\"Header for page 4\" data-page-number-auto=\"true\" style=\"text-align: left; position: absolute; top: 3224px; left: -75px; right: -75px; width: auto; margin: 0px; z-index: 6;\" data-page-number-format=\"page\" data-page-assist-positioned=\"true\">Page 4</div>"
  },
